{"tid":2247144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科技公司接連將在家工作恒常化！Dropbox將在家工作納入日常固定模式","createTime":"2020-10-17T15:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T15:13:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49a6132663d11a5fc12dda08cb42fc098e169ddb","tid":2247144,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Xv.i5TDB.qg1jbp.Ldswyw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant/business_digest_949/776668db938b09efda3840acf1783eba\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXv.i5TDB.qg1jbp.Ldswyw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant%2Fbusiness_digest_949%2F776668db938b09efda3840acf1783eba&h=ee221788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前，微軟（Microsoft）宣布在疫情緩和後員工也可選在家工作。雲端儲存服務公司Dropbox日前在官網發文，宣布該企將成為「Virtual First」企業，將遙距工作納入日常固定模式。這是繼微軟後又一家將在家工作恆常的企業。<br />\n<br />\nDropbox對員工進行內部調查，接近90%員工表示，在家工作能提高生產效率，並不想回到每周5天上班的固定工作模式。在疫情下，在家工作變成常態，不少企業正採取混合模式。Dropbox認為不同員工的取向，可能導致業績、個人升遷等不公現象浮現，故該企宣布成為「Virtual First」公司，以遙距工作為主導，呈現分散式的工作型態。<br />\n<br />\n「Virtual First」政策還包括採取「非線性工作日」，Dropbox希望在不同時區的員工可在重疊工作時間以外，根據個人需要自行安排適合的時間表。該企業還計劃改造全球13個辦公室成「Dropbox Studios」，供所有員工使用，以進行團隊聚會、面談等。"},{"pid":"befe1b27c6137e29f4d669db0bc771628106a267","tid":2247144,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"如果香港公司都實行永久wfh，可能會變7X24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370b06203449c91258d906eac241b2d55c7ca2fd","tid":2247144,"uid":77968,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"befe1b27c6137e29f4d669db0bc771628106a267","tid":2247144,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"如果香港公司都實行永久wfh，可能會變7X24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:13:00.000Z","msg":"係365x24<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為放左假就唔使做野?"}]}